{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/room_caravan_decorate.gif?t=1738320177\" />In this cozy room decoration game you play as Dalia, a young witch returning home after university. As you clean and decorate beautiful areas to your liking, you will help the town and the magical creatures that inhabit it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/header_customizableobjects.gif?t=1738320177\" />Immerse yourself in relaxing gameplay with no timers as you decorate areas at your own pace. With a touch of magic you can adjust colors, sizes and magical effects to create the coziest spaces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/header_meetyourcoven.png?t=1738320177\" />Learn why Rue's caf\u00e9 is so messy, or what are gnomes scared of, as you restore balance to the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/header_creativemode.gif?t=1738320177\" />All the rooms, furniture and hundreds of objects available for you to play with! Be creative and make any Magic Room you can dream.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We'd love to see what you make \ud83d\udc96</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390130/extras/header_features.png?t=1738320177\" />\ud83d\udd2e Story mode - Help the town as you decorate multiple\u00a0 areas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfa8 Creative Mode - Create your own rooms with hundreds of objects at your fingertips.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph